UPDATE Listing SET description = '# Boat Bar: A Charming Oasis by the Water in Koh Samui

## Top Reviews
> **The Guy (5/5/5)**
> Tucked away off the main road, Boat Bar offers a peaceful escape from the tourist hustle. The location is perfect—right by the water with stunning views of the bay and bobbing boats, especially beautiful at sunset. It’s not loud; they keep the music low or none during quieter times, making it ideal for a calm, enjoyable meal without any blasting speakers or crowds. The prices are very reasonable—great value for the quality and setting. They have a well-balanced menu featuring both authentic Thai dishes and solid Western options, so there''s something for everyone.
> We ordered a chicken burger, fried wings, a beef burger, pad krapow (spicy basil stir-fry), and Tom Yum soup with seafood. Everything was delicious: the burgers were juicy and perfectly cooked, the pad krapow packed with bold flavors, and the Tom Yum was rich, tangy, with fresh seafood. Portions were decent for the price. The wings were a standout—super good, tender, and crispy. Service was friendly and attentive without being overbearing. Overall, Boat Bar is a charming little spot with excellent prices, good service, delicious food, and that rare peaceful vibe overlooking the bay. Highly recommend if you''re looking for a relaxed meal away from the noise.

> **Kevin Foster (5/5/5)**
> Fun bamboo bar on the beach. Great sunsets and nice staff. The beer is always cold and their food is the best around for the price.

> **Stephanie Mcgowan (1/5/5)**
> Menu looked good, but the chicken taco''s came with duck pancakes—definitely not tacos—and were very bland. The chicken burger had a funny purple color in it, and the chips were terrible (old oil) tasting of gasoline. Would not recommend or come back.

## E-E-A-T Signals
- **Expertise:** Boat Bar is run by California Chris, an American with a passion for his place who ensures guests have a welcoming experience.
- **Experience:** The bar offers a unique setting with stunning views and a peaceful atmosphere, perfect for a relaxing meal or drinks.
- **Authenticity:** The menu features both authentic Thai dishes and solid Western options, catering to diverse tastes.
- **Trustworthiness:** Positive reviews from satisfied customers highlight the quality of food, service, and overall experience.

### Primary Category: Restaurants (cmqyzwjo70005iuxdq6twl89w)
### Secondary Categories: Bars & Nightlife (cmqyzwjoc0007iuxd34aa6tf1), Gastronomy (cmqyzwjnj0004iuxd4b6k6akx)', categoryId = 'cmqyzwjo70005iuxdq6twl89w', secondaryCategories = 'bars--nightlife,gastronomy' WHERE id = 'cmr07ig50004wq8xd7f763200';
