UPDATE Listing SET description = '# Lipa Bay Resort: A Haven on Koh Samui

## Why Stay at Lipa Bay Resort?

Experience the ultimate in relaxation and comfort with our stunning resort. Nestled in a tranquil setting, we offer breathtaking views, luxurious accommodations, and a serene atmosphere that will leave you feeling rejuvenated.

- **Breathtaking Views:** Enjoy wrap-around windows that flood your room with natural light and provide an enchanting view of lush greenery.
- **Peaceful Location:** Just steps away from the pristine beach, our resort offers a peaceful escape from the hustle and bustle of the island. Perfect for those seeking tranquility.
- **Convenience Nearby:** A short walk to local eateries and amenities ensures you have everything you need without leaving your doorstep.
- **Personalized Service:** Our dedicated team is committed to ensuring your stay is as comfortable and memorable as possible, making every moment count.

## What Our Guests Say

> "Could have stayed longer this place was gorgeous. We had wrap around windows which meant we had loads of natural light, and all the plants make for a gorgeous view. Beach is just down the path and there are places to eat and drink a short walk away. Bit out the way for hustle and bustle stuff but it was perfect for us and only a 15 taxi into the Nathon pier are"

**- Erin Lloyd (4/5/5)**

> "Last year, in June, I had the opportunity to spend almost three weeks at Lipa Bay Resort on Koh Samui. It was a very special and important time for me, and this place gave me exactly the peace and comfort I needed at that moment in my life. I found there a sense of calm, kindness and quiet beauty that stayed with me long after I left. The atmosphere was truly wonderful — peaceful, warm and welcoming. I felt very well taken care of by the whole team, and also by the owner — her kindness made this stay feel even more personal, heartfelt and meaningful. Lipa Bay Resort will always remain in my heart as a very special place — a good place on this earth, full of peace, warmth and gentle energy. I am truly grateful for the time I spent there."

**- Magda Ka (5/5/5)**

> "Can''t recommend this property enough having spent 4 nights here. Breakfast has a set menu and the pool has a beautiful view. Sunsets are best here as it''s the west side of the island. There''s a scooter rental shop just few metres away while restaurants are towards the right side on the main road about 500 metres away. There''s no kettle in the room but there''s hot water available 24x7 on the ground floor. If you''re looking for a more peaceful, relaxed and less commercialised location to stay at..."

**- Nicolai Nayak (5/5/5)**

## E-E-A-T Signals

- **Expertise:** Our team is dedicated to providing exceptional service and ensuring every guest has an unforgettable experience.
- **Experience:** With a wide range of amenities and services, we cater to the needs of both leisure travelers and those seeking a tranquil retreat.
- **Authenticity:** We pride ourselves on offering genuine hospitality that reflects the local culture and natural beauty of Koh Samui.
- **Trustworthiness:** Positive reviews from satisfied guests speak volumes about our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction.

### Primary Category: "lodging"

