UPDATE Listing SET description = '# Samui Elephant Haven: Ethical Elephant Sanctuary in Koh Samui

## About Us
Samui Elephant Haven is a leading ethical elephant sanctuary located on the beautiful island of Koh Samui, Thailand. Founded by Maew Suriya with a dream to create an environment where rescued elephants can live freely and happily, our sanctuary has become a home for 14 rescued elephants since its opening in August 2018.

## Key Services & Features
- **Rescue and Rehabilitation**: We rescue elephants from challenging circumstances such as trekking camps and the logging industry.
- **Volunteer Programs**: Join us for a day of meaningful volunteer work, helping with daily elephant care routines like cleaning enclosures and preparing food.
- **Educational Tours**: Experience an immersive day tour to learn about elephant behaviors and witness these magnificent creatures living their happy lives in a natural setting.

## Why Choose Us?
Our team is dedicated to the well-being of our elephants, ensuring they live in a spacious, free-roaming environment. We prioritize love over profit, making Samui Elephant Haven an ethical sanctuary where visitors can connect with rescued elephants without intruding on their space.

### Call-to-Action
Book your visit today and experience the joy of these incredible animals up close!', categoryId = 'cmqyzwjol000biuxdry5pd9y1', secondaryCategories = '' WHERE id = 'cmr07ihm400p1q8xd8md4fi78';
UPDATE Listing SET description = '# Samui Elephant Sanctuary

## About Us
Samui Elephant Sanctuary is a pioneering ethical elephant sanctuary on Koh Samui in Southern Thailand. Since our establishment in Bophut in 2018, we have grown to Chaweng Noi, expanding our mission to rescue and care for more elephants. Our sanctuary offers a safe and natural environment where rescued elephants can thrive.

## Key Services
- **Morning or Afternoon Programs**: Join us for an unforgettable 3-hour experience with rescued elephants.
- **Short Elephant Encounter**: A 1.5-hour tour at Bophut, allowing you to walk alongside the elephants and observe their natural behaviors.
- **Sponsor Our Elephants**: Support our mission by sponsoring the daily care and food needs of our rescued elephants.

## Why Choose Us?
Our sanctuary is a model for ethical elephant tourism, adhering to high standards of animal welfare. We are proud members of the Saddle Off Model community, ensuring that elephants can live free from riding, shows, and exploitation. Our expert team has years of experience in elephant conservation and care.

## Book Your Visit Today!
Visit us at Samui Elephant Sanctuary for an unforgettable experience with rescued elephants. [Book Now](https://www.samuielephantsanctuary.org/book-a-visit)', categoryId = 'cmqyzwjop000eiuxdmebir1p7', secondaryCategories = '' WHERE id = 'cmr07ihm600p2q8xdym5l9l0k';
